introduction: Couple-swapping galore steams up the screen in this erotic tale of rock stardom, wealth, and naughty nurses. INSATIABLE NEEDS follows the story of one Dax Payne, a hunky musician whose band is on the brink of being the next big thing. Suddenly, however, Dax falls ill with a mysterious disease, and a sexy nurse named Kate is hired to care of him. It is not long before his new helper finds her way from the bedside to the bed, while Kate's abandoned fiance, himself quite easy on the eyes, seeks sensual solace in the welcoming arms of a coworker.
